section.heading: Chapter 74.42 RCW suspended—Effective date delayed until January 1, 1981

content.p: Print RCWs > Title 74 > Chapter 74.42 > Section 74.42.920 74.42.910 << 74.42.920 >> End of Chapter PDF RCW 74.42.920 Chapter 74.42 RCW suspended — Effective date delayed until January 1, 1981. Chapter 74.42 RCW shall be suspended immediately, and its effective date delayed so that it shall take effect on January 1, 1981. [ 1980 c 184 s 19 ; 1979 ex.s. c 211 s 72 .] NOTES: Effective date — 1980 c 184 s 19: "Section 19 of this 1980 act is necessary for the immediate preservation of the public peace, health, and safety, the support of the state government and its existing public institutions, and shall take effect immediately [April 4, 1980]." [ 1980 c 184 s 22 .]
